WEBVTT

00:01.240 --> 00:03.072
<i>Take a look around you right now.</i>

00:03.680 --> 00:06.559
<i>There's one thing everyone
who's come out here tonight has in common.</i>

00:07.320 --> 00:08.356
<i>Defiance.</i>

00:09.200 --> 00:10.200
<i>But it's more than that.</i>

00:11.320 --> 00:12.959
<i>You didn't just opt out</i>

00:13.400 --> 00:15.710
<i>of the creatures and the curfew</i>

00:16.400 --> 00:18.790
<i>of the rules and restrictions
that come with it.</i>

00:19.480 --> 00:21.551
<i>No, you went further than that.</i>

00:22.080 --> 00:23.080
<i>You opted in.</i>

00:24.040 --> 00:25.759
<i>Now, nothing about the race is easy.</i>

00:25.840 --> 00:27.752
<i>But it is going to be worth it.</i>

00:28.600 --> 00:31.832
<i>Cos at the end of tonight,
one team is gonna come with me</i>

00:31.880 --> 00:36.557
<i>to a place where you can sit out at night
and gaze up at the stars.</i>

00:37.960 --> 00:39.394
<i>A place without creatures.</i>

00:40.640 --> 00:41.756
<i>A place with hope.</i>

00:43.080 --> 00:44.116
<i>Good luck, people.</i>

00:45.280 --> 00:46.714
<i>Race yourselves free.</i>

